  "title": "Admin & Accounts Executive (Corporate Support) #80833",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Technology Services</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Admin & Accounts Executive (Corporate Support)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Joo Chiat</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday, 9.00am - 6.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary</strong></li><li>Duration: 3 Months Contract</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle AP/AR payments, bank updates, petty cash, and filing of invoices/receipts.</li><li>Support audits, trade finance, and government grant applications.</li><li>Provide HR admin support, including employee records, work pass updates, onboarding, and training coordination.</li><li>Maintain and update HR policies, employee handbook, and organisation chart.</li><li>Arrange travel, insurance renewals, and office-related purchases.</li><li>Coordinate with IT on systems, backups, equipment setup, and basic user support.</li><li>Ensure office HSE compliance, manage supplies, vendors, and general office maintenance.</li><li>Organise meetings, events, and name card/office stationery printing.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or equivalent, preferably in Business Administration or a related field.</li><li>Minimum 2 years’ experience in office administration, corporate support or HR support.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office and Windows.</li><li>Organised, meticulous, and able to manage multiple tasks independently.</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills with a proactive, responsible attitude.</li><li>No regular travel required, except for occasional company trips.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80833 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
